{"tid":2496090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Now新聞台工程人員遭警暴索償 高級警司莫慶榮指自己負責訓練警察「打暴動」","createTime":"2021-04-19T14:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T15:17:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4532c1a8c8a57f6524d67afd9c8ceec71e06bb3b","tid":2496090,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台工程人員李小龍指2014年在佔旺區採訪期間，突遭警員搶走鋁梯，及後遭指控襲警被捕。李小龍入稟向警方索償，自言被制服時遭警員施襲。辯方傳召當日有份制服李的警司，警司供稱見涉案警員被鋁梯打後，「轉身指住佢（李），係（被打後）好自然嘅反應」；又指李用梯打到警員後向後移的反應，「就好似做錯嘢咁」。<br />\n<br />\n現為警務處高級警司、機動部隊副校長的莫慶榮指，自己負責訓練警察「打暴動」的工作。他供稱當日協助執達吏清理旺角山東街、上海街交界的路障，其間看到李小龍跑入一群示威者中，並站在莫的左邊。<br />\n<br />\n莫在辯方主問時供稱他靠識別防暴頭盔，確認被指襲擊李的紅背包男子是警員，又指「呢種頭盔係警察先有嘅」。莫供稱當時從力度和角度，判斷李有意地襲擊警員，指李將梯掃向警員的右腳位置，形容謂：「見到梯的力度較大，唔係一般碰撞嘅意思，係有意嘅！」<br />\n<br />\n莫又稱從警員和李分別的反應，可反映出警員被襲擊。莫描述警員當時被梯打到後，轉身並指著李，莫認為「被打後指住佢（李）係好自然嘅反應」。另外，莫又指李將梯掃向警員後，即時後退，莫續指「就好似做錯嘢咁，就要即刻走啦」。<br />\n<br />\n莫供稱，涉被鋁梯打的警員在與李糾纏時，曾失平衡向後跌，而莫就伸手從後扶著該警員，糾纏其間莫亦再次見到李用梯打該警員。<br />\n<br />\n莫解釋，因李曾用鋁梯作武器襲擊警員，故他當時認為要控制李手上的鋁梯，並向李作出制服。其後莫將李交給同袍處理，自己繼續控制現場環境。案件明續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/FOWPB3GNGBEILJ44EUXRO72T3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2FFOWPB3GNGBEILJ44EUXRO72T3U%2F&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuHyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=30cba4d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2FFOWPB3GNGBEILJ44EUXRO72T3U%2F&h=0acf7eb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/FOWPB3GNGBEILJ44EUXRO72T3U/</a>"},{"pid":"5c21a4cff6aac9c7145b332329cd122b08f51573","tid":2496090,"uid":39710,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"死黑狗俾假口供"},{"pid":"cac1df57e3adda2ec9fd236df72c5c6435a5718e","tid":2496090,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcf10d6e8a040590b008acfcd4d77e6f25bc9c8","tid":2496090,"uid":265839,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:44:05.000Z","msg":"黑狗恐怖分子，襲擊平民"},{"pid":"7d9d79c2543cbda0836b61810672973c42c24921","tid":2496090,"uid":166474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:44:53.000Z","msg":"用鋁梯襲警但係七年都未落charge??"},{"pid":"4eb95d9b66189f841e4643b09274431402629740","tid":2496090,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb39f467b9ff52eb009cd289d5baa3c5a86caba","tid":2496090,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:49:09.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"f69a3bae3678c4b8e69b55b9afccfca14ab0087f","tid":2496090,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d548881fe30fdcfce68dd7e69143f9c3a72562","tid":2496090,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kung-06_uM0ue_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkung-06_uM0ue_1200x0.png&h=8f370f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c1317ae2f6f5e83ddd9c9bb196648144b7f2e0","tid":2496090,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"垃圾食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/f